Create a custom iterator which implement the [AutoCloseable interface](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/AutoCloseable.html)

    public interface CloseableIterator&lt;T&gt; extends Iterator&lt;T&gt;, AutoCloseable {
